snippet.title: GoldenEye X - Patch 6a Official Trailer
snippet.description:
It's been a long time coming, but the trailer for the next GoldenEye X mod release is finally here!  Take a gander at the mission campaign, which currently stands at nine levels.  Also see some of new options and bonuses that have been included since patch 5e dropped.  This version (6a) will be coming out soon.  Hopefully during this month of January.  I am still tinkering, and having people test it.  But be on the lookout at either the N64 Vault website, or the GoldenEye Mods Twitter (X) page, for more info!

http://n64vault.com/
https://twitter.com/GoldeneyeMods

I'm unable to log into the GoldenEye X N64 YouTube channel, so the trailer had to go up on my personal one.  Maybe we can get that sorted out another time.  Looking at you, YouTube...

Special thanks to TH126 for making this video!
http://www.youtube.com/th126

Part of the Frigate X song is from AlDavisMusic
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4wncKLYvxgo
